follow noopener\">https://show1show.com</a><br /><br />在全民 Vibe Coding 的时代，敲出几行代码生成一个“能跑”的软件原型确实变得轻而易举。但这种低门槛带来的副作用也日益凸显：产品同质化严重，且冷启动获客极其困难。很多优秀的创意在生成后，往往因为缺乏曝光而迅速沉寂，导致开发者无法获取真实用户反馈，产品迭代陷入死循环。<br /><br />为了解决这一痛点，我通过 Vibe Coding 开发了 “秀一秀” —— 一个专注于 Vibe Coding 作品的展示与发现平台。<br /><br />秀一秀 旨在降低开发者分享作品的摩擦力，无需注册和登录即可直接提交你的网站、App 、游戏或 AI 工具。平台不仅展示最终成品，还鼓励记录开发过程，帮助开发者获取早期用户关注与反馈。<br /><br />如果您不想亲自提交，也可以在这里留下作品信息，由我来代劳。", "last_modified": 1780667469, "replies": 48, "id": 1218305}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10992, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2345, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 703436, "username": "sport123", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sport123", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_mini.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_normal.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_large.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xlarge.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xxlarge.png?m=1760059769", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8553/4395/703436_xxxlarge.png?m=1760059769", "created": 1722386576, "last_modified": 1760059769, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sport123", "last_touched": 1780741844, "title": "人过 30 岁真的不是为自己而活了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1218371", "created": 1780714383, "deleted": 0, "content": "生活实在是太现实了", "conte